nodes.text: Xucaabo was a male Dug who worked for Sebolto during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. He was also employed by the Pixelito Puppeteers Union, and was a skilled and well-known puppeteer. A bounty was placed on his head by the Senator of Malastare, Ask Aak, for falling heavily on debt. In 32 BBY, the bounty, worth 3,500 credits for a live capture, and three thousand for deceased delivery, was claimed by the Mandalorian-turned Bounty hunter Jango Fett.
